WEBVTT

1
00:00:05.519 --> 00:00:08.519
Good news. Your father is no longer in danger.

2
00:00:08.519 --> 00:00:13.810
He does need to remain hospitalized for a few more days, but he should make a full recovery.

3
00:00:13.810 --> 00:00:14.939
Thank you.

4
00:00:14.939 --> 00:00:15.939
You're my choice.

5
00:00:15.939 --> 00:00:26.000
You should go home and rest.

6
00:00:26.000 --> 00:00:30.000
Trust me, I'll get your father home from the hospital today, on medical parole.

7
00:00:30.000 --> 00:00:35.670
Thank you.

8
00:00:35.670 --> 00:00:44.329
Don't wait up for me tonight, okay?

9
00:00:44.329 --> 00:00:49.299
I don't know how I can repay you.

10
00:00:49.299 --> 00:00:52.390
I think you do.

